1. Kupila sam nove *šale* za zimu. (I bought new scarves for winter.)
2. Oni *šalevi* koje si mi pričao nisu mi bili smiješni. (Those jokes you told me weren't funny to me.)
3. *Šal* od kašmira je jako mekan. (A cashmere scarf is very soft.)
4. Nije lijepo kad se nekome rugaš na *šal* koji nosi. (It's not nice to make fun of someone's scarf.)
5. Sinoć sam se smrzao jer nisam ponio *šal*. (Last night, I was cold because I didn't bring a scarf.)
6. Ona *šalica* kave je bila jako ukusna. (That cup of coffee was very tasty.)
7. Volim *šaliti se* s prijateljima. (I like to joke around with my friends.)
8. Ne mogu vjerovati da si *se šalio* kad si mi to rekao. (I can't believe you were joking when you told me that.)
9. *Šaljivdžija* je uvijek spreman na šalu. (The joker is always ready for a joke.)
10. Pustili su me iz bolnice jer je bila samo *lažna uzbuna*. (They released me from the hospital because it was just a false alarm.)